    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udcbc $17,500 - A no-nonsense, budget-friendly ride for the practical buyer! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, getting you where you need to go without any fuss. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and the signs of a well-used life, which is exactly reflected in the honest price. If you're looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank, this one deserves a look! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 17500.0,
