      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride without breaking the bank? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably and gets you from point A to point B without drama! It does show its age with some visible wear on the interior and exterior, and there are a few minor mechanical quirks you'll want to be aware of. For the budget-conscious driver who doesn't mind a little character, this could be a great everyday commuter at a price that makes sense!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 A budget-friendly opportunity for the right buyer! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has seen better days, with noticeable wear, cosmetic damage, and mechanical issues that will need attention. It may still be drivable, but expect to put some work (and money) into it. Perfect for a hands-on DIY mechanic, a parts sourcer, or someone looking for a project car at a rock-bottom price. What you see is what you get \u2014 priced accordingly and honestly!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and transparent picture before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 expect fading paint, some scratches, and possibly minor dents in a few panels. It's not a showroom car, but the body is structurally sound with no major rust or collision damage that would compromise integrity. Inside, the cabin reflects its age and use \u2014 the upholstery has worn spots and there may be some scuffs on trim pieces, though the layout and controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or minor repairs may be needed in the near term \u2014 think aging belts, seals, or suspension components that are due for attention. This is a solid choice for a buyer looking for reliable transportation on a budget who doesn't mind putting a little work in, but it is not suited for someone expecting a turn-key, worry-free experience without any investment beyond the purchase price.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in genuine mint condition \u2014 a designation we use only when a car truly earns it, and this one absolutely does. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains a deep, lustrous finish with no visible scratches, chips, or fading, and the body panels are straight and true with no signs of prior collision repair or bodywork. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with clean, unworn upholstery, a spotless headliner, and all trim pieces intact and tight. Every button, switch, and control functions exactly as intended, and the climate, audio, and infotainment systems all operate without issue. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have substantial tread remaining and are evenly worn, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is the kind of car that is genuinely difficult to find \u2014 one that has been exceptionally well cared for and shows it in every detail. Ideal for a buyer who wants a vehicle that drives and presents as close to new as possible without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained used car that presents nicely and drives reliably. The exterior shows only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with normal everyday use, such as light surface scratches and small door dings, but no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains a reasonable shine and the body panels align properly. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; upholstery shows moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but there are no tears, stains, or broken components. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are in good working order, and the car starts and drives without issues. Some minor maintenance items may be due in the near future, as expected with a used vehicle of this age, but nothing that would prevent safe, everyday driving. A solid choice for a buyer seeking a dependable used car without the premium price of a mint-condition example.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    }
